profile: Mason Place is family owned and operated. Our showroom is located on 25987 Woodbine Avenue Keswick, Ontario. We offer the best in wood burning and gas brands with many stoves, fireplaces inserts, BBQ, smokers and more in our showroom. Installations are done by WETT certified and qualified technicians each with decades of experience. Come visit our showroom or browse through our gallery of products available on our website.
